prevent ip stuff 
open robloxapp in x32dbg
go to symbols
select robloxapp
click string search, all modules
search "connection accepted", "connection from", "lost connection from", "Disconnect from" one at a time.
double click on it
right click -> follow in dump -> robloxapp.(random offset)
select the %s at the end of the string (ex:connection from %s)
replace %s with null bytes "00" in dump.
do the same thing for the others.

